@startuml
title Use Case: Manage Personnel

actor "HR Manager" as HR
actor "Police Chief" as PC
actor "Training Officer" as TO

usecase "Manage Personnel" as UC

HR --> UC : maintains records
PC --> UC : views/approves changes
TO --> UC : updates training

UC .> (Update Records) : include
UC .> (Assign Duties) : include
UC .> (Track Training) : include
UC .> (Process Changes) : include

UC <.. (Background Check) : extend <<new hires>>
UC <.. (Promotion Review) : extend <<promotions>>
UC <.. (Disciplinary Action) : extend <<performance issues>>

note right of UC
  Manages officer careers
  Tracks qualifications
  Ensures legal compliance
  Impacts daily operations
end note
@enduml
